      <p>The Association has noted that quite a number of street trees have been removed due to their deteriorating condition. The policy for Council owned trees is that if a tree is removed due to subsidence it will not normally be replaced at the same location. However if it was removed due to being diseased then they would consider planting a replacement.</p>
